## What This Skill Does Not Do

- It does not rewrite for strategy or positioning — that is a separate conversation.
- It does not replace the humanizer. Run humanizer first if the copy shows AI patterns; run this skill after.
- It does not make judgment calls about what to say — only about how to say it per Sydecar's rules.
- It does not apply to internal Slack messages or informal team communications.
